      "writtenOn": "2017-12-01T19:42:03Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I see, thanks.\n\nI\u0027m not overly concerned about the title not matching href; isn\u0027t that fairly common?\n\nRich tooltip with link to latest build sounds fine (with disclaimer that we don\u0027t know how it looks yet, may find it\u0027s too cluttered/fussy-looking in implementation).\n\nI\u0027m also fine just with \"\u003cbuilder ID\u003e (\u003cbuild ID\u003e)\" as mentioned earlier, if you\u0027re all OK with a bit of stutter.",
